Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Update nix to 0.29.0 to fix build on loongarch64

---
 Cargo.lock          | 38 ++++++++++++++++----------------------
 Cargo.toml          |  9 ++++-----
 src/service/core.rs |  2 +-
 3 files changed, 21 insertions(+), 28 deletions(-)

diff --git a/Cargo.lock b/Cargo.lock
index b8aa438..8fc75fa 100644
--- a/Cargo.lock
+++ b/Cargo.lock
@@ -125,6 +125,12 @@ version = "1.0.0"
